      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Crimson Moonlight",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Some knights from the Order\r\nhave reported that they have\r\nMalzeno surrounded in the Citadel.\r\nWe\u0027re unsure how long they\u0027re\r\nable to keep it there, so I\u0027m\r\ndispatching you immediately\r\nto handle the situation!",
        "Target": "Slay Malzeno",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Clair de lune pourpre",
        "Client": "Dame Fiorayne",
        "Description": "L\u0027\u00E9quipe de recherche locale\r\na pi\u00E9g\u00E9 un Malzeno. Ce\r\nsont des cr\u00E9atures dangereuses,\r\nce qui fait que je pense que\r\ncette mission te conviendrait\r\nbien mieux qu\u0027\u00E0 moi,\r\nau vu de ton exp\u00E9rience !",
        "Target": "Tuer Malzeno",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Chiaro di luna cremisi",
        "Client": "Dama Fiorayne",
        "Description": "La squadra di ricerca locale\r\nriferisce di aver intrappolato\r\nun Malzeno. Sappiamo quanto\r\nsia pericoloso, quindi pensavo\r\nche ci vorrebbe qualcuno con\r\npi\u00F9 esperienza nella caccia di\r\nme... Quindi ho pensato a te.",
        "Target": "Uccidi il Malzeno",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Karmesinrotes Mondlicht",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Einige Ritter des Ordens haben\r\nberichtet, dass sie einen Malzeno\r\nin der Zitadelle umzingelt haben.\r\nWir sind unsicher, wie lange sie\r\nihn dort halten k\u00F6nnen, daher\r\nschicke ich dich sofort los,\r\num die Situation zu kl\u00E4ren!",
        "Target": "Erlege den Malzeno.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Luna carmes\u00ED",
        "Client": "Fiorayne",
        "Description": "Algunos caballeros de la Orden\r\nnos informan de que han rodeado\r\na Malzeno en el Basti\u00F3n. No\r\nsabemos cu\u00E1nto tiempo lo podr\u00E1n\r\nmantener all\u00ED, \u00A1as\u00ED que te env\u00EDo\r\ninmediatamente para que te\r\nencargues de la situaci\u00F3n!",
        "Target": "Abate a Malzeno",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0410\u043B\u044B\u0439 \u0441\u0432\u0435\u0442 \u043B\u0443\u043D\u044B",
        "Client": "\u0420\u044B\u0446\u0430\u0440\u044C \u0424\u0438\u043E\u0440\u0430\u0439\u043D\u0430",
        "Description": "\u041C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043D\u0430\u044F \u044D\u043A\u043E-\u0433\u0440\u0443\u043F\u043F\u0430 \u0434\u043E\u043B\u043E\u0436\u0438\u043B\u0430 \u043E\r\n\u043F\u043E\u0438\u043C\u043A\u0435 \u041C\u0430\u043B\u0437\u0435\u043D\u043E. \u041C\u044B \u0432\u0441\u0435 \u0437\u043D\u0430\u0435\u043C,\r\n\u043A\u0430\u043A \u043E\u043D \u043E\u043F\u0430\u0441\u0435\u043D, \u0442\u0430\u043A \u0447\u0442\u043E,\r\n\u0432\u043E\u0437\u043C\u043E\u0436\u043D\u043E, \u0434\u043B\u044F \u044D\u0442\u043E\u0433\u043E \u0437\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043D\u0438\u044F\r\n\u043B\u0443\u0447\u0448\u0435 \u043F\u043E\u0434\u043E\u0439\u0434\u0435\u0442 \u043E\u043F\u044B\u0442\u043D\u044B\u0439\r\n\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u043D\u0438\u043A, \u0432\u0440\u043E\u0434\u0435 \u0432\u0430\u0441?",
        "Target": "\u0423\u0431\u0438\u0442\u044C \u041C\u0430\u043B\u0437\u0435\u043D\u043E",
